quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  26,141,Samuudunim‚Äô (Annabi Salihu niriba) daa labsi (Naawuni) tuumba  íirinima
  26,142,"Saha shőĶli b…õ mabia Salihu ni daa yőĶli ba: ‚ÄúDi ni b…ĒŇč…Ē, yi ku zo Naawuni?‚ÄĚ"
  26,143,‚ÄúAchiika! Mani ny…õla tuun‚Äô so Ňäun ny…õ y…õmbahigalana n-tin ya.‚ÄĚ
  26,144,"‚ÄúDinzu…£u, zom ya Naawuni ka doli ma.‚ÄĚ"
  26,145,"‚ÄúYaha! Mani bi b…Ēhiri ya sanyo‚Äô shőĶli, n-ka sanyoo m-pahila binnamda Duuma sani.‚ÄĚ"
  26,146,"‚ÄúDi ni b…ĒŇč…Ē, b…õ ni chan ya (Dunia) Ňč…Ē maa puuni, ka yi kuli mali yőĶmbahiga  íiya?‚ÄĚ"
  26,147,‚ÄúPuri mini kobilnina puuni (ka b…õ kuli y…õn ch…õn ya)
  26,148,"‚ÄúNi bindira, n-ti pahi dobino binwola din bi.‚ÄĚ"
  26,149,"‚ÄúYaha! Ka yi kpőĶri zoya puuni ka di leeri yiya n-ti ya, ka ny…õla di baŇčdiba.‚ÄĚ"
  26,150,"‚ÄúDinzu…£u, zom ya Naawuni ka doli ma.‚ÄĚ"
  26,151,‚ÄúYaha! Miri ya ka yi doli ban sa…£inda (barinanim‚Äô) yőĶlt…Ē…£a.‚ÄĚ
  26,152,"‚ÄúNinvu…£u shőĶba ban sa…£indi tiŇčgbani yaaŇča zu…£u, ka bi maanda.‚ÄĚ"
  26,153,"Ka b…õ yőĶli: ‚ÄúAchiika! A shiri be shirku ni gbaai shőĶba ni.‚ÄĚ"
  26,154,"‚ÄúA pala sh…õli m-pahila ninsala ti tatabo, dinzu…£u a yi shiri ny…õla yőĶlimaŇčlilana, t…Ē! Nyini tahimi ti alaama shőĶli na.‚ÄĚ"
  26,155,"Ka o (Annabi SńĀlihu) yőĶli: ‚ÄúNaawuni laakumi m-b…ĒŇč…Ē, ka o mali o kom nyubu dabsili (m…Ē…£ili Ňč…Ē ni), ka yi gba mali yi nyubu dabsili ka sokam mi li (dinzu…£u miri ya ka yi tooi m…Ē…£ili maa kom na…£ila yi nyubu dali).‚ÄĚ"
  26,156,"‚ÄúYaha! Di niŇč ya o (laakumi maa) bi…õrim shőĶli, ka dabsi‚Äô titali la daazaaba ti gbaai ya.‚ÄĚ"
  26,157,"Ka b…õ ku o (Laakumi maa), ka leei ninvu…£u shőĶba ban yoli tőĶm"
  26,158,Ka azaaba gbaai ba. Achiika! Ňä…Ē maa puuni mali kpahimbu. Amaa! B…õ (chőĶfurinim‚Äô) pam pala ban ti Naawuni yőĶlimaŇčli
  26,159,"Yaha! (Yaa nyini Annabi)! Achiika! A Duuma (Naawuni) ny…õla NyőĶŇčda, Zaddali Namb…Ēzobonaa"